00:26:37,409 --> 00:26:38,910
Hati-hati. Panas sekali.

440
00:26:40,537 --> 00:26:41,663
Yang akan datang.

441
00:26:42,372 --> 00:26:44,124
- Selamat menikmati.
- Terima kasih.

442
00:26:49,129 --> 00:26:51,464
Akhirnya kami mendapat beberapa pelanggan hari ini.

443
