Kebaikan.

577
00:34:16,826 --> 00:34:18,411
Jangan khawatir, kamu akan baik-baik saja.

578
00:34:20,204 --> 00:34:21,372
Kopi ini rasanya enak sekali.

579
00:34:21,455 --> 00:34:22,498
Silakan muat.

580
00:34:48,232 --> 00:34:49,233
Dia datang.

581
00:34:52,778 --> 00:34:53,779
Dia datang sendirian.

582
00:35:00,077 --> 00:35:01,162
Mari kita mulai.

583
