588
00:35:38,074 --> 00:35:40,159
Mengapa mereka harus bertemu di malam hari?

589
00:35:42,245 --> 00:35:43,579
Nah, begitulah.

590
00:35:48,209 --> 00:35:49,627
Ya, saya sudah sampai.

591
00:35:49,710 --> 00:35:51,796
