612
00:36:49,812 --> 00:36:50,855
Namun sekali lagi,

613
00:36:50,938 --> 00:36:54,692
Sekadar melihat uang saja sudah memicu keserakahan.

614
00:36:54,775 --> 00:36:56,152
APEL KEBERUNTUNGAN

615
00:37:03,743 --> 00:37:05,578
